OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FThe rapper formerly known as Kanye
OL,7,FWest has postponed an upcoming show in
OL,8,FMarseille, after French authorities
OL,9,Fsaid they would seek to ban the
OL,10,Fconcert over the artist's history of
OL,11,Fantisemitic remarks.
OL,13,FThe decision by Ye, as West is now
OL,14,Fknown, came a week after he was banned
OL,15,Ffrom entering the UK to headline the
OL,16,FWireless Festival in July, following a
OL,17,Fsimilar backlash in this country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
