OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776272751
OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,F"After much thought and consideration,
OL,7,Fit is my sole decision to postpone my
OL,8,Fshow in Marseille, France until
OL,9,Ffurther notice," Ye wrote on Wednesday
OL,10,Fon X.
OL,12,F"I know it takes time to understand
OL,13,Fthe sincerity of my commitment to make
OL,14,Famends."
OL,16,FThe rapper, who changed his name in
OL,17,F2021, had been expected to play at
OL,18,FMarseille's Stade Velodrome on June 11.
