OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776272751
OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FFrench Interior Minister Laurent Nunez
OL,7,Fhad pledged to explore "all
OL,8,Fpossibilities" to make sure the show
OL,9,Fwould not go on as planned, according
OL,10,Fto his office.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, Marseille Mayor
OL,13,FBenoit Payan opposed the rapper's
OL,14,Fvisit to one of France's most
OL,15,Fmulticultural cities.
OL,26,@nD@dTwoD@XOUpD@NO]uD@Est
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
