OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776272751
OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,F"I refuse to let Marseille be a
OL,7,Fshowcase for those who promote hatred
OL,8,Fand unabashed Nazism," Payan said.
OL,9,F"Kanye West is not welcome at the
OL,10,FVelodrome, our temple of community and
OL,11,Fhome to all Marseillais."
OL,13,FYe has drawn widespread condemnation
OL,14,Ffor making antisemitic remarks and
OL,15,Fvoicing admiration for Adolf Hitler.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]qD@AOUrD@BrrsD@YO]
