OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FYe released a song called "Heil
OL,7,FHitler" and advertised a swastika T-
OL,8,Fshirt for sale on his website last
OL,9,Fyear. Officials in Australia cancelled
OL,10,Fthe musician's visa in July after the
OL,11,Frelease of the single.
OL,13,FThe 48-year-old apologised in January
OL,14,Fwith a letter published as a full-page
OL,15,Fadvertisement in The Wall Street
OL,16,FJournal.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@GO]
