OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FHe said his bipolar disorder led him
OL,7,Fto fall into "a four-month-long, manic
OL,8,Fepisode of psychotic, paranoid and
OL,9,Fimpulsive behaviour that destroyed my
OL,10,Flife."
