OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776272751
OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FYe said in his latest message on X, "I
OL,7,Ftake full responsibility for what's
OL,8,Fmine but I don't want to put my fans
OL,9,Fin the middle of it. My fans are
OL,10,Feverything to me. Looking forward to
OL,11,Fthe next shows. See you at the top of
OL,12,Fthe globe."
OL,14,FThe refusal to allow Ye into the UK
OL,15,Fled to the cancellation of Wireless
OL,16,Ffestival.
OL,18,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said the
OL,19,FGold Digger rapper should never have
OL,20,Fbeen invited to headline the festival.
OL,26,@nD@eOUtD@KO]
