OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FThe prime minister said: "Kanye West
OL,7,Fshould never have been invited to
OL,8,Fheadline Wireless.
OL,10,F"This Government stands firmly with
OL,11,Fthe Jewish community and we will not
OL,12,Fstop in our fight to confront and
OL,13,Fdefeat the poison of antisemitism.
OL,15,F"We will always take the action
OL,16,Fnecessary to protect the public and
OL,17,Fuphold our values."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@SO]
