OL,3,CKanye West postpones French show after
OL,4,CUK visa rejected
OL,6,FIt is understood that the Mayor of
OL,7,FLondon's office had refused permission
OL,8,Ffor the London Stadium in Stratford to
OL,9,Fstage a West concert this summer, with
OL,10,Fsources citing community concerns and
OL,11,Fthe reputational impact on the city.
